# ECS Directory

This directory is intended for the Entity-Component-System (ECS) implementation of the Three-G project.

- Place all ECS-related source files here.
- Include documentation and usage examples as needed.

## Structure

- `components/` - Component definitions
- `systems/` - System logic
- `entities/` - Entity management

## Getting Started

1. Add new components in the `components/` folder.
2. Implement systems in the `systems/` folder.
3. Manage entities in the `entities/` folder.

For more details, refer to the main project documentation.